---
// docs.osirisjson.org is launched initially light-only to align to osirisjson.org
// no toggle exists anywhere in the UI, so just force the theme instead of running Starlight's stock
// localStorage/prefers-color-scheme detection (which would otherwise still
// flip visitors with OS-level dark mode into Starlight's dark tokens).
---

<script is:inline>
	document.documentElement.dataset.theme = 'light';
</script>
